beer.beer_description: Hawthorn Amber Ale is a rich malt flavoured ale. The inclusion of Marris Otter base malt ensures a lovely rounded body, whilst a small addition of chocolate malt in the grain bill delivers a warm bittersweet roasted caramel flavour. Mild English hops balance the sweet malt and plenty of dry hopping infuses a floral and spice aroma. Dark auburn in colour, it is smooth and well balanced. Drink it a few degrees warmer than the fridge for the full flavoured experience
